avatartranslator

Class AvatarLibraryFunction

  • java.lang.Object
    • avatartranslator.AvatarElement
      • avatartranslator.AvatarLibraryFunction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AvatarStateMachineOwner, AvatarTranslator

    public class AvatarLibraryFunction
extends AvatarElement
implements AvatarTranslator, AvatarStateMachineOwner
    AvatarLibraryFunction is used to represent a library function that can be further used in state machine diagrams.

    A library function is defined by:

    • a name
    • a set of AvatarAttribute representing the parameters of the function,
    • a set of AvatarAttribute for local usage,
    • a set of AvatarSignal that are used to communicate,
    • a set of AvatarAttribute that will contain the return values of the function and
    • an AvatarStateMachine that describes the content of the function.
